                        </layoutDesc> 
                         
                    </objectDesc>
                    
                    <handDesc>
                        <handNote>The texts in the three strups were written by different scribed, at least two different hands.</handNote>
                    </handDesc>
                    
                    <decoDesc>
                        <decoNote type="miniature"><locus>After line 36</locus>: magical letters' frame</decoNote>
                        <decoNote type="miniature"><locus>After line 158</locus>: Demon Legewon bound with a red cord. It is written in the miniature: "As Legewon was reduced to disgrace".</decoNote>
                        <decoNote>Miniatures are made in colour. There were originally three but the first one was cut off.</decoNote>
                    </decoDesc>
                    
